<h1>Introduction</h1>
<p>Ailib is a unified multi-provider AI SDK for Rust: one API surface for 17+ model providers with streaming, multimodal, function & tool calls, routing, reliability primitives and observability foundations — with &lt;1ms SDK overhead.</p>
<p><strong>Key goals:</strong></p>
<ul>
  <li>Single interface, no vendor lock-in</li>
  <li>Deterministic overhead &lt; 1ms</li>
  <li>Progressive complexity (simple chat → advanced routing)</li>
  <li>Reliability & performance baked in (retry, fallback, race, batching)</li>
  <li>Extensible: custom providers, middleware, strategy plug points</li>
</ul>
<p>Continue with <a href="/docs/getting-started">Getting Started</a>.</p>
